invalid type: string "I know there's still a\\Nlittle goodness left in you!\nLet us through!\nNow!\nOr what?\nAre they going to humiliate\\Nme at my wedding?\nShrink up like an\\Ninsect and get into a jar?\nShould I join a book club, too?\nWe had a great time, Mario!\nBut Bowser is back!\nAnd they will feel my full fury!\nDad!\nI am the lord of bones!\nI am the skeleton king!\nAnd I am his son!\n.